<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0151001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0151001">漢譯南傳大藏經第二十九卷第二四七頁、一〇七之蘆鬘施者參照。</note>
<note n="0154001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0154001">底本兩足主……人中之牛王均為業格，今依暹羅本為呼格。</note>
<note n="0155002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155002">多羅之行樹，底本為 tālapattī，今採用脚註本及暹羅本之 tālapanti。</note>
<note n="0158001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0158001">第三八三譬喻（前卷四四〇～四四一頁）參照。</note>
<note n="0159001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0159001">第二一二譬喻（前卷三〇〇頁）參照。</note>
<note n="0159002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0159002">巴那底（pānadhi）意義不詳，見於斯提德氏巴英字典以 pānada = upāhanā，應為一種草履。</note>
<note n="0161001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0161001">瓦達麋加（vatamigo）羚羊之一種。</note>
<note n="0161002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0161002">圍裙我取砂，採用暹羅本之 ucchaṅgena puḷinaṁ gayha。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
